title: Coheed and Cambria discography (as of June 2008)
description:
The Second Stage Turbine Blade


In Keeping Secrets of Silent Earth: 3


Good Apollo, I&#039;m Burning Star IV Vol. 1: From Fear Through the Eyes of Madness


Good Apollo, I&#039;m Burning Star IV Vol. 2: No World for Tomorrow


Live at La Zona Rosa [EP]


String Quartet Tribute to Coheed and Cambria (ok, so this isn&#039;t actually a Co & Ca album, but it&#039;s some pretty awesome string quartet rendition of the In Keeping Secrets album)


If you like this music you should check out cobaltandcalcium.com, which is the Co & Ca fan site. The story (as pieced together by fans and through what Claudio has told us) is on there. You should also check out the Amory Wars comic books which tell the story that these albums tell in comic book form.


This is a great band that makes music different from anything else that&#039;s out there, they deserve our support.
